        <mxCell id="LQwCk8dbOmhS_KGoKl8P-35" parent="1" style="shape=note;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UUID&lt;/strong&gt; significa &lt;strong&gt;Universally Unique Identifier&lt;/strong&gt; (Identificador Único Universal). Es básicamente un código muy largo y prácticamente irrepetible, con esta pinta:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;question_id&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;tu sistema va a procesar datasets con 100+ preguntas de golpe (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;search_dataset&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;answer_dataset&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;). Cada pregunta necesita un identificador único para que, más adelante, en &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;evaluate&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;, puedas decir &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&quot;la respuesta que generé para la pregunta X coincide (o no) con la solución correcta de la pregunta X&quot;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="360" x="320" y="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="LQwCk8dbOmhS_KGoKl8P-37" parent="1" style="shape=note;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Una &lt;b&gt;clase abstracta&lt;/b&gt; es la forma de decirle a Python: esta clase existe solo para que otras hereden de ella y la completen, nadie deberia poder crear una instancia de ella.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Obligas que cualquier chunker nuevo que crees en el futuro(Ejm: JsonChunker) tenga que implementar obligatoriamente el método &lt;b&gt;chunk&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="210" x="-750" y="-840" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
